CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 17, reads: "Slums Growing in Homewood? - Untidy Yard - Sheer neglect, as shown in this unkept back yard facing an alley behind the 7400 block of Race St., is one of the conditions which the Homewood Community Improvement Association hopes to improve."
TitMainTitle: Two story brick house with clothesline, shrubs, and debris in dirt yard, 7400 block of Race Street, Homewood
